{
  "stem": "8423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said-- they went to volunteer to the German [? women, ?] knocking on the window in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said, they're chefs from back home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Do they need any chefs?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they could cook, but they certainly weren't chefs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were hired.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when they saw me come into the kitchen, they said, we must hide every trace of this, because we can't make anything of it, or they'll take her away, meaning me, and all this sort of stuff.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they tried to clean me up the best I could, but I did lose a tooth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, we just were told, which I-- just not talk about, not make anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because any incident like this that happened there, there was some kind of evidence, you know, of them, their wrongdoing, or whatever, they just took you away.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in this place where I was able to steal some bread, even for my friends at night, before I left the kitchen to go to my barrack.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my barracks were full of these people from the factories who were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could even steal some bread or save my own ration, because I ate other things in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, my sister would save me some vegetables and things from the kitchen, you know, where she was-- where she was peeling.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we would bring the bones from the kitchen, because now this was the meals for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got the peels in our soup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would bring the bones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they would eat the marrow from the bones and little gristle that was left on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we'd be exchanging food all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
